<shortdesc>Use the <keyword conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/vbnmdpv"/> verb to
verify an ISO-1 <ph rev="sh20i1">or,  beginning with Release 5.4, an ISO-4 format PIN,</ph> in a
transaction. The account, the card data, and the PRW are used to verify the PIN.</shortdesc>
