  <refbody>
    <section>
      <p>The input PIN is converted to PBF-0 format. A test PIN reference value (PRW) is created and
        that value is compared bit by bit to the input PRW.</p>
<note rev="sh20i1">This verb supports <keyword
conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/pcihsm2016"/> compliant-tagged key tokens.</note>
    </section>
